==English==
===Etymology===
*(1) Vulgar Latin ''limitaris'' of a threshold
*(2) '''Lin'''ux and In'''tel'''

===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɪntəl|-ɪntəl]]

===Noun===
#{{architecture}} A [[horizontal]] [[structural]] [[member]] spanning an [[opening]], such as between the [[upright]]s of a [[door]].
#{{computing}} The [[computing]] [[environment]] of the [[Linux]] [[operating system]] running on an [[Intel]] [[CPU]]; mostly in a [[server]].

